This paper discusses the properties and metrics of information, which are relevant to information theory (cs.IT), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new model and metrics for information, which could be of interest to researchers in these sub-categories.
